References: <D43896D7.26490%g-feng@northwestern.edu>
Message-ID: <3d4166ff-87a6-49a2-921a-36f8f1282440@roswellpark.org>

I updated the code to remove the R CMD check error (svn revision  
r123826) and to clean up miscellaneous NOTEs about formatting (r123827).  
I ported these changes to release.

It is likely that the package has a number of other similar problems  
(assigning exprs() with incompatible dimnames) so a thorough review is  
required.

There are vignette products in the vignettes/ directory, but no Rnw /  
Rmd files; this needs to be corrected.

If there is no-one willing to actively maintain this package, I think  
that it should be deprecated in devel. This would impact a number of  
packages that Depend, Import, or Suggest lumi.

Martin

